                  <paragraph>Dispense in well-closed container with child-resistant closure.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Store at controlled room temperature 20°-25°C (68°-77°F)[See USP Controlled Room Temperature].</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Distributed by:<br/>
